lass="list-item">                 <div class="list-item__number">4</div>                 <div class="list-item__text">Ian is an animal lover. He has two rescue cats who are adorable creatures. They made lockdown so much easier for him with their companionship.</div>             </div>                      <div class="list-item">                 <div class="list-item__number">5</div>                 <div class="list-item__text">He adores computer games. For Ian, being able to escape reality is essential. He believes enjoying immersive storylines whilst applying strategy to solving easier problems than poker is a great way to unwind!</div>             </div>         </div>         <div class="content__image">                                              <picture>                  <img src="/assets/Ian-Simpson-pic-1656502872322_tcm1488-561250.png" width="428" height="530" alt="5 Facts You Didn’t Know About Ian…" loading="lazy">     </picture>          </div>     </div> </div> </div>               </div>      </div> </div></div> <div class="container responsivegrid">  <div class="">     <div class="container-wrapper main-container">                             <div id="container-fd50e4112a" class="cmp-container">                                </div>      </div> </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div><?php include_once ($_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"]."/footer.php"); ?>